name: William Cadeli
description: I consider myself to be a normal, easy going, sensitive and fun person and would like to meet someone who is interested in starting a relationship. Endless first dates are really not that much fun!! The woman I would like to date should enjoy similar interests as myself as it is very important to have things in common and that we both enjoy doing together. I would like to meet someone nice, sweet, normal and fun as well. Physical attraction is important
